				\begin{document}$$V = - \frac{1}{{C\left( x \right)}}Q + {V_{OC}}\left( x \right)$$\end{document}

Under short-circuit (SC) conditions, charges will transform between the two electrodes by to offset the potential difference. Eq. 2 can be utilized to express this condition.1820=-1CxQSCx+VOCx\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
